title: COVID-19 Vaccine Side Effects & Injuries - CHD's Community Forum
cleaned_text:
Welcome! We are so excited you're here. In a world where our community is being repeatedly censored and groups with thousands of members are being removed online, we want to make it easy for you to find your community, get plugged in, start a discussion, ask questions, organize and connect with people just like you. There is power in numbers and if the powers at large can keep us from joining together, they can restrict the reach of our message.





On the Community Forum, you do not have to "speak in code." You can use your name or remain anonymous, engage in discussion or simply observe, so put your carrot emojis away and join our community!
